1978;;Wolf Lake;;American;;Burt Kennedy;;Rod Steiger, David Huffman, Robin Mattson;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wolf_Lake_(film);;The story follows a group of men traveling to a duck hunt in the Northwest. One of them, Charlie, is hoping to travel and forget the grief he has over his son's death in Vietnam. When he learns a young member of his party, David, is a deserter, Charlie goes berserk and hunts David.